NAME
.br
.ti +5
libo1 - terminal I/O library for the Osborne 1
.sp
DESCRIPTION
.br
.in +5
LIBO1 provides a standard interface to cursor manipulation
functions available with the Osborne 1 computer.
.sp
Some of the functions provided are listed below:
.sp
.in +3
.br
clrscrn	- home the cursor and clear the screen
.br
eralin	- erase a line
.br
homcur - home cursor
.br
movcur	- move cursor to adjacent position
.br
setcur	- set the cursor to a coordinate position
.sp
.ti -3
Other functions which may be unique to the Osborne are:
.sp
erteol - erase to end of line
.br
graphics - place terminal in graphics mode
.br
normal	- place terminal in power up mode
.sp
.in -3
.br
The use of these functions to control cursor operations on any
suitable CRT is one approach to providing more portable code.
.sp
.ti -5
